{"tid":1374193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突擊！係唯一一個方法光復元朗","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:46:21.000Z","uid":166287,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10808d55021e690f23d311398d96cb6d84d30fdd","tid":1374193,"uid":166287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"經過今日！大家雖然有晒準備，但係我地既計劃實在係太張揚，講真你地既裝備有幾多個扑過一下差佬，擋過一下子彈？就算係元朗遊行一百萬次都只係會比班牛屎佬笑，因為佢地有晒警察保護，再出黎打多我地幾獲都仲得。<br />\n<br />\n所以仇就一定要報，係依個咁荒謬既社會，正路行唔通就要行捷徑，分別組隊突襲元朗村，攻擊佢地最重視既野。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣先可以比D顏色班牛屎佬睇下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇反應再組隊，希望30個一隊，</span>"},{"pid":"998c624c961c7fc746228dd1b55b44cdfcbb8238","tid":1374193,"uid":166287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94e87a7bef7d3581ee926082f9354fbd7ae0aaa","tid":1374193,"uid":166287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1dd1e643e47719bec7ab679c1250896f1a0553","tid":1374193,"uid":166287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75304f2c357223a99528e100a7729